Martin,

Pull the one you have, measure it and then go buy one long enough to 
make the difference.

If long enough is not available, look at the extensions/ends  that the 
dune buggy folks use when theirs are all too long and they have to cut 
them and fit a new end.

http://www2.cip1.com/ProductDetails.asp?ProductCode=ACC%2DC10%2D2565

